event_name: After Hours, by Protocol Labs (hosted by Ramo) 5/5
description:
Join us for laid-back evenings (~7pm-midnight) of connection and conversation with members of the Protocol Labs network! This casual after-hours event is open to anyone, from founders and innovators to open-source contributors and tech enthusiasts. It’s the perfect chance to unwind and engage in meaningful discussions about the projects and ideas that excite you the most—whether it’s web3, AI, AR/VR, BCI, and more.

​With many startups, foundations, and research groups in the network, this is an opportunity to meet fellow members, explore collaborations, and share your passion in a relaxed atmosphere. There’s no agenda—just good vibes, great company, and space to brainstorm or simply hang out.
